Along with the rapturous depictions of the #stellersseaeagle dive bombing unwitting NE cod, I want to see comparisons to a submarine captain in search of glory, sailing into the too-shallow waters of an unfriendly harbor.

Bird alert accounts have greatly improved my quality of life. But they are very respectful and I do sometimes wish for more anthropomorphism in their postings. I want to hear guesses about the #stellersseaeagle’s existential dread, knowing it will never again see home again.
